featurePrompt: Build a padel club management system

files.description: Management dashboard page for club admins to manage club, courts, users, and bookings.
Shows current club (tenant) info at the top of the management dashboard.
Manage courts: list, add, edit, delete courts for the club.
Manage users: list, add, edit, delete users for the club.
Manage bookings: list, add, edit, delete bookings for the club.
